INSERT INTO public.sample_essays VALUES ('0432d9b4-1629-4992-9846-93f9d57aabbb', '[FORECAST WRITING] Dự Đoán IELTS WRITING TUẦN (18/5-25/5)', 'forecast-writing-du-doan-ielts-writing-tuan-185-255', '<h1 dir="ltr"><strong>Dự đoán IELTS Writing Task 1-2 tháng 5 (18/5 - 25/5)</strong></h1>
<p dir="ltr">Lưu ý: Dự đoán có bạn trúng có bạn không do số đề random rất nhiều, đây chỉ nên là các đề dùng để tham khảo trước khi thi nhưng AD vẫn mong là các bạn sẽ trúng phần nào đó. Chúc các bạn học tốt.</p>
<p>Nếu bạn cần sample hoặc muốn gợi ý viết nhanh trong 30 phút, hãy sử dụng Chat Bot<a href="https://chatgpt.com/g/g-NfjggXjSs-ielts-prediction-ai"> IELTS Prediction</a> nhé — nó sẽ soạn đúng theo đề bạn sắp thi. Chúc bạn đạt đúng aim trong kỳ thi cuối năm!</p>
<p> </p>
<p>TASK 2</p>
<p dir="ltr"><strong>Technology &amp; Media</strong></p>
<ol>
<li dir="ltr" aria-level="1">
<p dir="ltr" role="presentation">Newspapers are having enormous influence on people''s ideas and opinions. Why is this the case? Is it a positive or negative situation?</p>
</li>
<li dir="ltr" aria-level="1">
<p dir="ltr" role="presentation">Some people have benefited from modern communications technology, but some other people have not benefited from; to what extent do you agree or disagree?</p>
</li>
<li dir="ltr" aria-level="1">
<p dir="ltr" role="presentation">Modern communications technology benefits some people but some don''t benefit at all. Do you agree or disagree?</p>
</li>
</ol>
<p dir="ltr"><strong>Society &amp; Family</strong></p>
<ol start="4">
<li dir="ltr" aria-level="1">
<p dir="ltr" role="presentation">Modern communications technology benefits some people but some don''t benefit at all. Do you agree or disagree?</p>
</li>
<li dir="ltr" aria-level="1">
<p dir="ltr" role="presentation">Nowadays, some parents put a lot of pressure on their children. What is the reason for this? Is this a positive or negative development for the children?</p>
</li>
<li dir="ltr" aria-level="1">
<p dir="ltr" role="presentation">Many people believe that family has the strongest influence on a child’s development, while others believe that external factors such as television, friends and music play a big role. Discuss both views.</p>
</li>
<li dir="ltr" aria-level="1">
<p dir="ltr" role="presentation">Some people choose to have their first child at an older age. What are the reasons? Do the advantages outweigh the disadvantages?</p>
</li>
<li dir="ltr" aria-level="1">
<p dir="ltr" role="presentation">Some people say that in the modern world, getting old is entirely bad. Others, however, say that life for the elderly nowadays is much better than it was in the past. Discuss both these views and give your own opinion.</p>
</li>
</ol>
<p dir="ltr"><strong>Government &amp; Culture</strong></p>
<ol start="9">
<li dir="ltr" aria-level="1">
<p dir="ltr" role="presentation">Many today feel that most urgent problems can only be solved by international cooperation. To what extent do you agree or disagree?</p>
</li>
<li dir="ltr" aria-level="1">
<p dir="ltr" role="presentation">Companies should provide sport and social facilities for local communities. To what extent do you agree?</p>
</li>
<li dir="ltr" aria-level="1">
<p dir="ltr" role="presentation">In many countries, the government likes to spend more money on the arts. Some people agree with this. However, others think the government should spend more on health and education. Discuss both sides and give your opinion.</p>
</li>
<li dir="ltr" aria-level="1">
<p dir="ltr" role="presentation">Watching a live performance such as a play, concert, or sporting event is more enjoyable than watching the same event on television. To what extent do you agree or disagree?</p>
</li>
<li dir="ltr" aria-level="1">
<p dir="ltr" role="presentation">It is important for all towns and cities to have large public spaces such as parks and squares. Do you agree or disagree with this statement?</p>
</li>
</ol>
<p dir="ltr"><strong>Environment &amp; Energy</strong></p>
<ol start="14">
<li dir="ltr" aria-level="1">
<p dir="ltr" role="presentation">Fossil fuels, such as coal, oil and natural gas, are the main source for many countries. However, some nations are using alternative energy such as solar power and wind power. Do you think this is a positive or negative development?</p>
</li>
</ol>
<p dir="ltr"><strong>Education</strong></p>
<ol start="15">
<li dir="ltr" aria-level="1">
<p dir="ltr" role="presentation">Students leave high school without learning how to manage their money. What are the reasons and solutions for this issue?</p>
</li>
</ol>
<hr>
<p dir="ltr"><strong>Question 1</strong></p>
<div dir="ltr" align="left">
<table style="width: 91.345%; border-collapse: collapse; border-width: 1px; border-spacing: 1px; height: 150px;" border="1"><colgroup><col style="width: 100%;" width="625"></colgroup>
<tbody>
<tr style="height: 150px;">
<td style="border-width: 1px; padding-top: 1px; padding-right: 1px; padding-bottom: 1px;">
<p style="padding-left: 40px;">The table below gives information about the population of people aged 60 and over in six regions in 2000 and the predicted figures for 2050. It also shows the world total of people aged 60 and over in 2000 and 2050.</p>
<p dir="ltr" style="padding-left: 40px;">Summarise the information by selecting and reporting the main features, and make comparisons where relevant.</p>
</td>
</tr>
</tbody>
</table>
</div>
<p dir="ltr" style="padding-left: 40px;">Write at least 150 words</p>
